These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: chess, monopoly, canasta, scrabble
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, aquamarine, amber, blue
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, soul, reggae, dubstep
1. the fan reggae is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the fan dubstep is the person who likes mauve##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
4. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is between the fan reggae and the person playing monopoly##2
6. the fan soul is the person who likes amber##1
7. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Game        | canasta | scrabble  | monopoly | chess  |
| Color         | blue    | aquamarine  | mauve       | amber     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | jazz | dubstep       | soul |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
City: berlin, paris, edinburgh, boston
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, dancer, scientist, engineer
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, grey, red, mauve
1. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes mauve is between the engineer and the person traveling to boston##2
5. the engineer is the person who likes grey##1
6. the architect is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
7. the scientist is the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| City         | paris | berlin    | boston  | edinburgh |
| Job   | engineer  | architect  | dancer   | scientist    |
| Color         | grey | mauve | turquise | red      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, davidoff, bolivar, aristoff
City: liverpool, san-francisco, colone, hannover
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, tram, roller, scooter
1. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the scooter and the davidoff-smoker##2
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar      | davidoff | aristoff         | dannemann   | bolivar    |
| City         | san-francisco | hannover | liverpool | colone |
| Transport   | roller   | tram        | scooter      | skateboard   |

