.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, mirinda, almond-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, action, mystery, thriller
House: craftsman, farmhouse, art-deco, townhouse
1. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
2. the craftsman house is between the townhouse house and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the craftsman house is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the townhouse house is between the person watching epic movies and the farmhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk        | fanta   | 7up | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre         | mystery | epic | action    | thriller |
| House     | art-deco       | craftsman     | townhouse       | farmhouse    |

