.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, zinnia, bellflower, iris
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, baccarat, bongani, tiparillo
4 different games are played: chess, billiard, whist, scrabble
1. the person playing scrabble is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growszinnia##2
2. the person playing scrabble is the person who growsiris##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing whist##1
6. the person playing whist is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
7. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing whist and the montecristo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Flower   | daffodil | iris      | zinnia       | bellflower   |
| Cigar      | montecristo   | baccarat  | tiparillo | bongani     |
| Game      | billiard     | scrabble | whist        | chess |

