.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, begonia, tulip, balloon-flower
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, baccarat, tiparillo, davidoff
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, helicopter, quad-bike
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the person driving the helicopter##2
6. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growstulip##2
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Flower    | tulip | begonia  | marigold | balloon-flower      |
| Cigar   | tiparillo  | davidoff  | aristoff | baccarat |
| Transport   | quad-bike | skateboard | snowmobile | helicopter     |

