.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, journalist, dressmaker, dancer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, lily, azalea, aconite
4 different games are played: go, scrabble, billiard, chess
1. the person playing chess is the person who growslily##1
2. the person playing billiard is the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the person playing go##1
6. the journalist is between the person who growslily and the person who growsazalea##2
7. the dancer is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job          | dressmaker  | journalist    | dancer | doctor  |
| Flower   | azalea | aconite       | lily        | marigold    |
| Game         | scrabble | go | chess  | billiard |

