.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, water, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, american, british, brazilian
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, bike, train, airplane
1. the brazilian is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the american is between the person driving the airplane and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the brazilian is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person drinking water is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate  | fanta | water | cola |
| Nationality   | canadian  | brazilian | american   | british         |
| Transport           | quad-bike | train  | bike   | airplane      |

