.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, snowmobile, quad-bike, taxi
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold, lily, bellflower
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, 7up
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is the person driving the train##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person who growslily is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
6. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who growsdaffodil##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Transport          | taxi  | train    | quad-bike | snowmobile       |
| Flower         | bellflower | marigold | daffodil  | lily |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate   | 7up      | iced-tea  | cola     |

