.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
4 different games are played: go, domino, chess, backgammon
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, lawyer, scientist, nurse
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, coffee, cola
1. the nurse is on the far left##1
2. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
3. the person playing domino is between the person playing go and the lawyer##2
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the scientist is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the person drinking cola is the nurse##1
8. the person drinking water is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Game          | chess      | backgammon | domino | go |
| Job         | nurse   | lawyer  | firefighter | scientist |
| Beverage   | cola | water   | hot-chocolate | coffee |

