.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
City: rome, miami, nizza, new-york
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, coffee, cola
House: ranch-style, tower, wooden, modern
1. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the wooden house is the person traveling to miami##1
3. the ranch-style house is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the person drinking coffee is between the ranch-style house and the person traveling to new-york##2
5. the person drinking coffee is the modern house##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is the tower house##1
7. the person drinking cola is the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| City    | new-york  | nizza | rome | miami     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | coffee   | cola  | sprite    |
| House     | tower        | modern       | ranch-style      | wooden |

