.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, western, martial-arts, satire
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, amaryllis, lily, rose
4 different games are played: go, backgammon, billiard, monopoly
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person who growsrose is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching western movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person who growsamaryllis##2
4. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person playing go is on the far right##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | martial-arts     | western | scientific       |
| Flower      | lily  | rose | poppy  | amaryllis |
| Game        | monopoly  | backgammon      | billiard        | go      |

