.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, salsa, funk, folk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, november, may, february
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, chaman, fonseca, blend
1. the fan folk is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is between the fan funk and the person who's birthday is in october##2
3. the fan salsa is on the right of the fan funk##1
4. the fan indie is the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the fan folk is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | folk  | funk       | salsa   |
| Birthday      | october     | may | november | february |
| Cigar        | fonseca        | blend | dunhill     | chaman |

