.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
4 different games are played: bridge, canasta, chess, poker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, december, june
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, handball, sailing, rugby
1. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person playing chess##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person playing chess##2
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
7. the person who's sport is handball is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Game           | canasta | poker | chess    | bridge   |
| Birthday   | december      | october   | june | september |
| Sport     | parkour     | handball       | sailing        | rugby    |

