.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, funk, blues
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, tea, iced-tea
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, chinese, colombian, dutch
1. the fan funk is the colombian##1
2. the dutch is the fan blues##1
3. the fan d&b is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the fan funk is on the far left##1
5. the chinese is between the person drinking coffee and the fan d&b##2
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the australian##1
7. the australian is between the dutch and the chinese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | gospel           | d&b         | blues      |
| Beverage     | coffee | tea | iced-tea | juice |
| Nationality   | colombian     | chinese         | australian       | dutch        |

