.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, traveling, video-games, sudoku
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike, scooter, subway
City: rome, berlin, new-york, edinburgh
1. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person traveling to berlin##2
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person driving the scooter and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person traveling to rome is between the person traveling to new-york and the person driving the subway##2
7. the person driving the quad-bike is the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Hobby      | traveling | video-games | singing   | sudoku |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | motorbike    | scooter   | subway     |
| City   | edinburgh  | new-york | rome | berlin   |

