4. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the indian##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
7. the indonesian is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
