4. the person driving the snowmobile is between the palace house and the cottage house##2
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person driving the airplane and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
7. the tower house is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
