3. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
4. the malaysian is the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the owner of the bird is the malaysian##1
6. the indian is between the owner of the hamster and the malaysian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
