.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, sailing, baseball, climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, paramedic, chef, manager
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, egyptian, japanese, american
1. the social-worker is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the paramedic##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the social-worker##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
5. the american is the manager##1
6. the paramedic is between the person who's sport is climbing and the japanese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport        | climbing | sailing | golf | baseball |
| Job         | social-worker       | paramedic     | chef   | manager   |
| Nationality   | nigerian | egyptian | japanese | american |

 